1 ($1, 500.00), or by imprisonment in the county jail not to exceed
2 sixty (60) days, or by both such fine and imprisonment.
3 H. Any person convicted of violating the provisions of this
4 section shall have the commercial hunting area upland game license
5 revoked. No new license shall be issued for a period of six (6)
